  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Business Pilot for Responsible ASM gold</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mauritania has a unique emerging ASGM sector. Gold was discovered in 2015 and it is estimated that 50,000 miners are currently involved in the Mauritanian mining sector. However, the sector is as of yet completely informal and lacks access to training, equipment and finance. Miners and forgerons (a craft which is prevalent in and unique to the Mauritanian mineral sector) rely on inefficient processing methods emitting large quantities of mercury, affecting human health and the environment.  As a result, supply chain transparency is very difficult to achieve.  The sector is also vulnerable to intrusion from insurgent groups in the Sahel region.</narrative>
  </description>
